{"tid":2035880,"cid":35,"subCid":0,"title":"(伏)電腦維修鋪","createTime":"2020-05-26T06:55:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-26T08:27:07.000Z","uid":239742,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"5ef71e852577f8b6a2e3d69f64ce9910d7b67c7d","tid":2035880,"uid":239742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T06:55:30.000Z","msg":"前日，我拎部手提電腦去維修。<br />\n我本身見Wifi界面卡有問題，就覺得應該好易整返好，所以拎左去附近維修。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n維修完<br />\nWifi卡仍然有問題，觸控板壞左，開機開好耐（試過開唔到機仲一直發熱，懷疑死機）<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n店主話系統相撞導致觸控板壞左用唔到，開機load得慢既解釋，update 左window頭幾次係load得慢啲。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n收左我150蚊<br />\n<br />\n佢拎到反屋企<br />\n開機睇下，冇反應，個部機不斷發熱。個種熱係用notebook差住電打左10幾場lol個種。大佬開個機姐。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我梗係9沖返去問佢，佢夾硬熄左部機再開返，又比佢開到，但load左成幾分鐘。<br />\n<br />\n收150蚊係合理，但唔包整壞部機㗎。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲要好理真氣壯同我講，你個觸控板壞左，你唔用既話，以後用滑鼠咪得。大佬，唔好呃我冇讀過書啦。依家擺明同我講，我整壞左你個觸控板，你以後用滑鼠啦7頭。<br />\n<br />\n唉唔開名，但個間店係大埔廣場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />名同財仔xx兄弟好似，不過前面唔係安信。<br />\n<br />\n老闆，勿相認。<br />\n如果真係見到呢個po，希望你去進修下，唔好再害人。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n部機用左一年炸，比你搞到咁，係我高估左你<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我都有錯既，錯在太心急<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d622b1b82b5c6f7d10affcffcf6c04c26ee2ade","tid":2035880,"uid":351202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T07:27:57.000Z","msg":"睇下有冇比人換到粒U<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7cec52c2045a0c9003b9fc146795cd7bedf0209","tid":2035880,"uid":239742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5d6